-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D320505138857250&d=h%2FjpO%2F4vOxs1xnBU3UKRHlDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=0efe3e42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=320505138857250</a><br />\n7.21 警察開槍射胡椒彈 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/471254926754367/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F471254926754367%2F&d=h%2FjpO%2F4vOxs1xnBU3UKRHlDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=d53205f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/471254926754367/</a><br />\n警再放催淚彈Stand News 立場新聞 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/450544468858025/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F450544468858025%2F&d=h%2FjpO%2F4vOxs1xnBU3UKRHlDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=52fe9854\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/450544468858025/</a><br />\n7.21 警察現場發放多枚催淚彈 22:20 Stand News 立場新聞 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/631475204017598/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F631475204017598%2F&d=h%2FjpO%2F4vOxs1xnBU3UKRHlDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=7fd00ff3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/631475204017598/</a><br />\n速龍小隊斥記者「係咪中立、係咪有立場」Stand News 立場新聞 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/679125395894103/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F679125395894103%2F&d=h%2FjpO%2F4vOxs1xnBU3UKRHlDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=63265be3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/679125395894103/</a><br />\n【7.21 現場】警察防線前的媽媽 Stand News 立場新聞 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/godblesshk/videos/583308962199292/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgodblesshk%2